<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Happy Birthday My Love💖</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0f0f0f, #1c1c1c);
      color: white;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .container {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      animation: fade 2s ease;
    }

    img {
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 4px solid white;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    p {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: auto;
      line-height: 1.7;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    button {
      margin-top: 25px;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 30px;
      background: white;
      color: black;
      font-size: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    button:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    @keyframes fade {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .heart {
      position: absolute;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      animation: float 5s linear infinite;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    @keyframes float {
      from {
        transform: translateY(100vh);
        opacity: 0;
      }
      to {
        transform: translateY(-10vh);
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <audio autoplay loop>
    <source src="CantikManis.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
  </audio>

  <div class="container">
    <img src="IMG-20260525-WA0012.jpg" alt="foto" />

    <h1>Happy Birthday 💖</h1>

    <p>
      Selamat ulang tahun yaa ✨<br><br>
      Semoga semua hal baik selalu datang ke hidup kamu,
      makin bahagia, makin cantik, makin kuat jalanin semuanya.
      Terima kasih udah hadir dan jadi orang spesial buat aku💕
    </p>

    <button onclick="alert('Aku cuma mau bilang... kamu berharga banget 💖')">
      Klik disini
    </button>
  </div>

  <script>
    for(let i = 0; i < 20; i++) {
      let heart = document.createElement('div');
      heart.className = 'heart';
      heart.innerHTML = '❤';
      heart.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + 'vw';
      heart.style.animationDuration = (Math.random() * 3 + 3) + 's';
      heart.style.fontSize = (Math.random() * 20 + 10) + 'px';
      document.body.appendChild(heart);
    }
  </script>

</body>
</html>
